```text
Continue from the previous zDash implementation.

Project: ⬡ zDash · FULL SYSTEM BLUEPRINT v2.0

Now execute ONLY:

PHASE 30 · FINAL ENDGAME RELEASE + ENTERPRISE BOARD PACK + ACQUISITION/IPO DOSSIER
Release Candidate Freeze + Executive Pack + Investor/Acquirer Dossier + Launch Command Center

IMPORTANT:
Inspect the repo first. Do not rebuild previous phases. Do not remove existing behavior. Create safe compatibility shims for missing modules.

GLOBAL SAFETY INVARIANTS:
- Endgame release, board pack, dossier, launch, and export workflows must be read-only, dry-run, or approval-gated by default.
- Generated packs must exclude secrets, private keys, raw credentials, customer-sensitive data, and raw payment data by default.
- Never enable live trading, real IoT, real social posting, secret export, or unsafe automation by default.
- Never bypass Guardian, content approval, RBAC, tenant isolation, certification, or deployment safety checks.

OBJECTIVE:
Build final endgame release layer:
1. Release candidate freeze and system-wide readiness rollup.
2. Enterprise board pack generator covering product, market, security, compliance, revenue, traction, risks, roadmap, and support readiness.
3. Acquisition/IPO dossier templates with sanitized metrics only.
4. Customer proof pack and launch command center.
5. Final launch checklist and LTS/maintenance plan.
6. Frontend Endgame Release page.

BACKEND MODULES:
- backend/app/endgame/{__init__.py,models.py,release_freeze.py,board_pack.py,dossier_builder.py,launch_checklist.py,endgame_service.py}
- backend/app/api/endgame.py

FRONTEND MODULES:
- frontend/src/pages/EndgameRelease.tsx
- frontend/src/components/endgame/{ReleaseFreezePanel.tsx,BoardPackPanel.tsx,DossierBuilderPanel.tsx,LaunchChecklist.tsx,EndgameReadinessCard.tsx}
