DELIVERABLES:
Repo inspection summary, files, tests, README, .env.example, docs, API examples, safety checklist, acceptance checklist, known limitations, and Phase 31 handoff.

Now generate Phase 30 and save this prompt into docs/prompts/phase30.prompt.
